com.tinkerpop.frames.modules

Interface TypeResolver

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GraphTypeManager, TypeManager

    public interface TypeResolver
    Allows dynamic resolution of interfaces that a frame will implement when framing an element. For instance the java type information may retrieved from a property on the element. Instances of this class should be threadsafe.
    Author:
    Bryn Cooke
